  "bodyHtml": "<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Return processing deadlines</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Return processing starts as soon as return tracking says the parcel has been delivered.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You must always comply with the return processing deadline, which is the time between the reception of the return and the implementation of the solution. This deadline is the same for all Sellers but varies according to the situation and product :</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 517px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 107px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Situation leading to the return</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Processing time </span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Withdrawal of the customer </span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2 business days to refund</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Repair or exchange an item (not laptop or home appliance)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3 business days</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Repair or exchange for Laptops, MacBooks and home appliances</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5 business days</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">For all repairs or exchanges, the tracking number (do not input the tracking link in the field) must be filled by the deadline, and the return shipment must be picked up by the carrier no later than the following business day to be considered on-time.</span></p>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">For large items, your customer can choose between 3 options: a home-repair appointment, an appointment to pick up the defective item and deliver a replacement, or an appointment to pick up the defective item and receive a refund.</span></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Return expected outcomes</strong></span></h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 242px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 160px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 66px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 70px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 87px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Situation</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Who decides?</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Repair</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refund</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Exchange</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 38.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Withdrawal</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client prior to return</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 38.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Wrong product received</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client prior to return</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 38.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1st defective product (repairable)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Seller</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 38.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1st defective product (non-repairable)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client after Seller asks </span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️ </span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 38.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Double defective product</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client prior to return</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">✔️ </span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Return processing checklist in case of issues</strong></span></h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 391px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 233px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 37pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Checklist action</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Processing times</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 29.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">☑️  Declare any delivery issue upon reception if any</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2 business days</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 80.5pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">☑️  Discard or declare warranty exclusion </span></p>\n<br><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In the event of warranty exclusion, you must declare the problem with the buttons in your Back Office interface</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Processing delay</span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2 business days in case of refund request</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3 business days in case of repair/replace</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<ul></ul>"
}